) VALUES (
  'Complete Guide to WhatsApp Business API in India (2026): Pricing, Setup, Automation & CRM',
  'whatsapp-business-api-india-guide-2026',
  'Learn how WhatsApp Business API works in India, including pricing, setup process, automation, CRM integration, and best practices to grow your business in 2026.',
  '[
    {"id":"b001","type":"paragraph","content":"In India, WhatsApp is not just a messaging app anymore — it has become a powerful business tool. From small startups to large enterprises, companies are using WhatsApp to communicate, sell, and support customers.\n\nBut if you want to scale your business communication, the normal WhatsApp Business app is not enough.\n\nThis is where **WhatsApp Business API** comes in.\n\nIn this complete guide, you will learn everything in simple English — what WhatsApp API is, how it works, pricing in India, setup process, automation, CRM integration, and best practices."},
    {"id":"b002","type":"heading","content":"What is WhatsApp Business API?","level":2},
    {"id":"b003","type":"paragraph","content":"WhatsApp Business API is an advanced solution provided by Meta that allows businesses to send messages at scale, automate conversations, and manage customer communication professionally.\n\nUnlike the regular WhatsApp Business app:\n- It does not run like a mobile app\n- It works through software platforms and APIs\n- It supports automation, integrations, and multiple users\n\nIn simple words: **WhatsApp API turns your WhatsApp into a full business communication system.**"},
    {"id":"b004","type":"heading","content":"Why WhatsApp API is Important for Businesses in India","level":2},
    {"id":"b005","type":"paragraph","content":"India has one of the largest WhatsApp user bases in the world. Customers prefer messaging over calls or emails. Here are the main benefits:"},
    {"id":"b006","type":"list","content":"","items":["**High Open Rates** — WhatsApp messages have an open rate of more than 90%, much higher than email or SMS.","**Faster Response** — Customers expect instant replies, which improves trust and satisfaction.","**Better Lead Conversion** — Quick replies lead to higher chances of closing sales.","**Automation Saves Time** — Businesses can automate replies, follow-ups, and notifications.","**Multi-Agent Support** — Teams can manage conversations together from one dashboard."],"ordered":false},
    {"id":"b007","type":"heading","content":"How WhatsApp Business API Works","level":2},
    {"id":"b008","type":"paragraph","content":"The WhatsApp API system has three main parts:"},
    {"id":"b009","type":"list","content":"","items":["**Meta (WhatsApp Owner)** — Meta provides the infrastructure and messaging system.","**API Providers** — Platforms like WATI, AiSensy, Gupshup, and [Aireatro](https://aireatro.com) provide dashboards and tools to use the API easily.","**Your Business System** — This includes your CRM, automation tools, and workflows."],"ordered":true},
    {"id":"b010","type":"heading","content":"WhatsApp API Pricing in India (2026)","level":2},
    {"id":"b011","type":"paragraph","content":"Understanding pricing is very important before starting.\n\n**Meta Conversation Charges**\nMeta charges businesses per conversation (24-hour window). Types of conversations include user-initiated (customer starts chat) and business-initiated (you start chat). Charges in India are relatively affordable compared to other countries.\n\n**Platform Fees**\nMost providers charge ₹999 to ₹14,999 per month with optional setup fees. Some modern platforms like [Aireatro](https://aireatro.com) offer ₹0 monthly fees — you pay only Meta charges."},
    {"id":"b012","type":"heading","content":"How to Get WhatsApp Business API in India","level":2},
    {"id":"b013","type":"paragraph","content":"Follow this step-by-step process:"},
    {"id":"b014","type":"list","content":"","items":["**Create Meta Business Account** — Sign up on Meta Business Manager.","**Verify Your Business** — Submit documents like GST, PAN, or company registration.","**Add a Phone Number** — Use a number not linked to WhatsApp before.","**Choose API Provider** — Select a platform that offers dashboard and tools.","**Connect Facebook Page** — Link your business page with WhatsApp.","**Create Message Templates** — Templates are required for sending notifications and campaigns.","**Go Live** — Start messaging customers and capturing leads."],"ordered":true},
    {"id":"b015","type":"heading","content":"WhatsApp Automation for Business Growth","level":2},
    {"id":"b016","type":"paragraph","content":"Automation is the biggest advantage of WhatsApp API. Here are the key automation features:"},
    {"id":"b017","type":"list","content":"","items":["**Auto Replies** — Send instant responses to new messages.","**Lead Capture Automation** — Automatically respond when a lead is generated.","**Chatbots** — Answer FAQs without human effort.","**Follow-up Messages** — Send reminders and updates automatically.","**Bulk Campaigns** — Send promotional messages using approved templates."],"ordered":false},
    {"id":"b018","type":"heading","content":"Example Automation Flow","level":3},
    {"id":"b019","type":"list","content":"","items":["User submits a form","Lead is captured","WhatsApp message is sent instantly","CRM stores the lead","Sales team follows up"],"ordered":true},
    {"id":"b020","type":"heading","content":"WhatsApp API with CRM Integration","level":2},
    {"id":"b021","type":"paragraph","content":"CRM integration makes WhatsApp API more powerful. CRM (Customer Relationship Management) helps manage customer data and interactions."},
    {"id":"b022","type":"list","content":"","items":["**Centralized Data** — All leads in one dashboard","**Team Collaboration** — Multiple agents manage chats","**Lead Tracking** — Track status and history","**Automation Workflows** — Trigger actions based on behavior"],"ordered":false},
    {"id":"b023","type":"heading","content":"Use Cases of WhatsApp API","level":2},
    {"id":"b024","type":"list","content":"","items":["**E-commerce** — Order updates, delivery tracking, support","**Real Estate** — Property inquiries, follow-ups","**Education** — Admissions, course details","**Services** — Appointments, reminders"],"ordered":false},
    {"id":"b025","type":"heading","content":"WhatsApp API Rules & Guidelines","level":2},
    {"id":"b026","type":"paragraph","content":"To avoid getting blocked, follow these rules:"},
    {"id":"b027","type":"list","content":"","items":["**Avoid Spam** — Do not send messages without user consent.","**Use Approved Templates** — Required for outbound messaging.","**Take User Permission** — Always get opt-in before messaging.","**Avoid Irrelevant Messaging** — Only send useful content."],"ordered":false},
    {"id":"b028","type":"heading","content":"WhatsApp API vs WhatsApp Business App","level":2},
    {"id":"b029","type":"paragraph","content":"| Feature | Business App | API |\n|---|---|---|\n| Multi-user | No | Yes |\n| Automation | No | Yes |\n| Bulk messaging | No | Yes |\n| CRM integration | No | Yes |\n| Scalability | Limited | High |"},
    {"id":"b030","type":"heading","content":"Best Practices for Success","level":2},
    {"id":"b031","type":"list","content":"","items":["**Respond Quickly** — Faster replies increase conversions.","**Personalize Messages** — Use customer name and context.","**Use Smart Automation** — Balance automation with human interaction.","**Track Performance** — Use analytics to improve campaigns."],"ordered":false},
    {"id":"b032","type":"heading","content":"Future of WhatsApp API in India","level":2},
    {"id":"b033","type":"paragraph","content":"WhatsApp API is growing fast in India. Future trends include AI-powered chatbots, full automation systems, and deeper CRM integrations. Businesses that adopt early will have a strong advantage."},
    {"id":"b034","type":"heading","content":"Conclusion","level":2},
    {"id":"b035","type":"paragraph","content":"WhatsApp Business API is a powerful tool for modern businesses in India. It helps you communicate faster, automate workflows, manage leads efficiently, and increase sales.\n\nIf you want to scale your business in 2026, WhatsApp API is not optional — **it is essential.**"},
    {"id":"b036","type":"cta","content":"","buttonText":"Start Using Aireatro — Zero Monthly Fees","buttonUrl":"/signup"}
  ]'::jsonb,
